+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
zm_zerbes_demons
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

Features:
64 Spawns
Cubemaps
2 Drivable Boats
2 German .88 FlaK
Drivable Helicopter
8 Secrets
Custom poster :)

Story:
It was just a little Concret Island in the middle of the Sea. So quiet and peaceful, but then this one container arrived and the massacre started.

Now its your Turn. Try to survive as long as u can. Baricade yourself in a house, climb on a roof or just hide yourself in the big underground area. 


A Note to Server Administrators:
This map has a point_servercommand inside it. Without it the boats will not work and the cannon won't function properly. If you have a point_servercommand override plugin, then you'll need to make a .cfg for this map with sv_turbophysics 0 in order for the boats and cannon to work.


Play this Map on this server:
[-b!p-] Deutscher Schlachthof @ FastDL [- blood-is-power.de -]
IP: 78.46.95.172:27615
